#: src/sbom.md:1
msgid "SBOM (Software Bill of Materials)"
msgstr ""

#: src/sbom.md:3
msgid ""
"Maturin can automatically generate [CycloneDX](https://cyclonedx.org/) SBOMs "
"and include them in the built wheel under the `.dist-info/sboms/` directory, "
"following the convention described in [PEP 770](https://peps.python.org/"
"pep-0770/)."
msgstr ""

